String in java:
    A string is a sequence of character . in java, string is a class present in the java.lang package 
    
    key point
    1. immutable
    2. stored in string constant pool
    3. any modification creates new object

    class StringExample{
        public static void main
    }

String buffer:
    StringBuilder is similar to StringBuffer but not thread safe.

    key point
    1. mutable
    2. thread safe

String builder:
    StringBuffer is used to create mutable String.

    key point
    1. mutable
    2. not thread safe


